Choose to focus on what you CAN do. Choose to see the good. Choose to believe in possibilities.

postTitle:
One must work without being driven solely by the anticipation of wealth. Seeking pleasure without a clear conscience has consequences. Knowledge is meaningless without character, and earning without morality often leads to downfall. Scientific greatness without humanity can be disastrous. Worship holds no value without sacrifice.

And above all ‚Äî politics must never be played without principles. It should always serve the greater good.

#SevenSocialSins #LeadWithValues #PurposeDrivenLeadership #IntegrityMatters
